translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,163,Ngempela sambula kuwena njengoba sambula kuNowa nakubaphrofethi abeza ngemva kwakhe futhi sembula ku- Abrahamu naku-Ishmayeli no-Isaka nakuJakobe nasezizweni nakuJesu nakuJobe nakuJona naku-Aron nakuSolomoni futhi sanikeza uDavide izabura (amahubo)
  4,164,Nezithunywa esasikutshenile ngazo ngaphambilini nezithunywa esingazange sikutshene ngazo futhi uMvelinqangi wakhuluma noMose
  4,165,(Sathumela) izithunywa njengabalethi bezindaba ezimnandi nabaxwayisi ukuze abantu bangabi nalo izwi lokuziphendulela kuMvelinqangi (emva kokufika) kwezithunywa futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani
  4,166,"Kepha uMvelinqangi uyafakaza ngalokho akwehlisela phansi kuwena, wakwehlisela phansi ngolwazi lwakhe nezingelosi ziyofakaza futhi uMvelinqangi wanele njengofakazi"
  4,167,Ngempela labo abangakholwanga futhi bavimba (abanye) endleleni kaMvelinqangi baduke ukuduka okukude le
  4,168,"Ngempela labo abangakholwanga futhi benza ukona, uMvelinqangi angeke abathethelele futhi angeke abaholele endleleni"
  4,169,Ngaphandle kwendlela yasesihogweni bayohlala khona lapho phakathi ingunaphakade futhi ngasosonke isikhathi lokho kuMvelinqangi kuyinto elula
  4,170,Oh Bantu! isithunywa sifikile kunina neqinio elivela eNkosini yenu ngakho-ke kholwani kungcono kunina kepha uma ningakholwa ngakho-ke ngempela kungokukaMvelinqangi konke okusemazulwini nokusemhlabeni futhi ngasosonke isikhathi uMvelinqangi uyazi unobuhlakani